{"title":"退出登录常用的方法","slug":"退出登录常用的方法","date":"2017-09-20T01:59:08.599Z","updated":"2017-09-16T05:11:49.694Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"退出登录时事件触发-正确的顺序\"><a href=\"#退出登录时事件触发-正确的顺序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"退出登录时事件触发(正确的顺序)\"></a>退出登录时事件触发(正确的顺序)</h2></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>清除session —&gt; 发送ajax请求；</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div><div class=\"line\">4</div><div class=\"line\">5</div><div class=\"line\">6</div><div class=\"line\">7</div><div class=\"line\">8</div><div class=\"line\">9</div><div class=\"line\">10</div><div class=\"line\">11</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$(.退出登录按钮).on(<span class=\"string\">\"click\"</span>,<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">    $.post(<span class=\"string\">\"数据库退出登录API\"</span>,&#123;&#125;,<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\">res</span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//后台会有业务逻辑清除session</span></div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//在回调函数(浏览器端)中清除cookie;(需要到入jquery.cookie.js)</span></div><div class=\"line\">        $.removeCookie(<span class=\"string\">\"键名\"</span>)</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//跳转到登录页面</span></div><div class=\"line\">        location.href = <span class=\"string\">\"login.html\"</span></div><div class=\"line\">    &#125;)</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n","categories":[{"name":"开发技巧","path":"api/categories/开发技巧.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"建站技巧","path":"api/tags/建站技巧.json"}]}